849
00:39:58,480 --> 00:40:01,780
Spending 500,000 yen will get you a 5000 yen gift certificate

850
00:40:01,780 --> 00:40:04,060
at this store specializing in bags

851
00:40:02,580 --> 00:40:05,170
Oh it's that kind of package

852
00:40:02,580 --> 00:40:05,170
That's pretty strict isn't it...

853
00:40:04,060 --> 00:40:08,480
Of course, we found numerous ridiculous point cards here...

854
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:14,020
...but within that, this is the one that beats the rest

855
00:40:14,730 --> 00:40:17,190
In Osaka, there's a maid cafe

856
00:40:17,190 --> 00:40:19,250
called "Nadia"

857
00:40:19,250 --> 00:40:24,240
They have a system where if you spend 500 yen, you earn one point

858
00:40:23,860 --> 00:40:25,920
There's a option for 500 points

859
00:40:24,240 --> 00:40:28,350
They have various prizes from 5 points to those with special privileges starting at 200 points

860
00:40:28,350 --> 00:40:30,880
Basically, if you exchange 100,000 yen worth of points

861
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:32,670
You get a photoshoot with the maids

862
00:40:33,130 --> 00:40:36,680
Furthermore, 150,000 yen will get you a lunch date with a maid.

863
00:40:36,680 --> 00:40:41,630
250,000 yen and you can hang out with a maid for an entire day.

864
00:40:41,630 --> 00:40:44,460
And the prices continue to rise.

865
00:40:43,210 --> 00:40:47,400
That's pretty cool

866
00:40:44,980 --> 00:40:47,830
There are still goals which require more points

867
00:40:47,830 --> 00:40:51,890
Taking a maid on a vacation in a foreign country will require 3000 points.

868
00:40:50,590 --> 00:40:53,070
Vacation to a foreign country?!

869
00:40:51,890 --> 00:40:56,550
(14.000 USD or 10.000 Pounds)

870
00:40:51,890 --> 00:40:56,550
In actuality, you need 1,500,000 yen in points.

871
00:40:55,090 --> 00:40:56,870
So expensive!

872
00:40:56,900 --> 00:41:01,610
However, you will not be able to go alone with a maid,

873
00:41:01,610 --> 00:41:04,070
The store owner will tag along with you.

874
00:41:02,720 --> 00:41:06,720
He comes along??

875
00:41:04,070 --> 00:41:07,000
In addition, all travel expenses

876
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:10,950
and accommodation charges will be covered by the customer.

877
00:41:10,950 --> 00:41:12,720
Who would wanna do this??

878
00:41:12,720 --> 00:41:18,520
Even though these rules being so strict, is there anyone who would take this trip?

879
00:41:18,870 --> 00:41:21,750
Has anyone ever saved up for the trip to a foreign country?

880
00:41:19,540 --> 00:41:21,750
What is this...

881
00:41:21,750 --> 00:41:24,670
Yeah, there have been a few

882
00:41:24,670 --> 00:41:31,240
I've tagged along to places like Hong Kong, Hawaii, and Paris.

883
00:41:31,810 --> 00:41:36,400
There have been 10 people so far that have earned this trip.

884
00:41:37,470 --> 00:41:40,850
By the way, of the customers currently in the maid cafe today

885
00:41:40,850 --> 00:41:43,970
How many points have they saved so far?

886
00:41:44,400 --> 00:41:46,420
We asked them to let us see their cards

887
00:41:45,060 --> 00:41:47,200
Noooo....

888
00:41:49,350 --> 00:41:51,890
308 points

889
00:41:50,520 --> 00:41:51,880
I see

890
00:41:51,970 --> 00:41:53,730
With a cost of 150,000 yen

891
00:41:53,730 --> 00:41:56,490
he's saved up over 300 points

892
00:41:56,490 --> 00:42:00,740
What can you get now that you've saved 300 points?

893
00:42:00,740 --> 00:42:02,910
I can go on a lunch date

894
00:42:02,910 --> 00:42:06,740
together with a maid to a store I like.

895
00:42:06,740 --> 00:42:08,470
What do you think? Are you gonna do it?

896
00:42:08,470 --> 00:42:11,350
I was thinking about it before, but now I'm reconsidering

897
00:42:11,350 --> 00:42:15,400
Because I can go to several places if I use 500 points.

898
00:42:12,370 --> 00:42:14,300
He's so serious

899
00:42:15,400 --> 00:42:17,890
I see, so these 300 points

900
00:42:17,890 --> 00:42:21,520
If I use them once, they'll decrease

901
00:42:21,810 --> 00:42:23,060
How much have you spent so far?

902
00:42:23,060 --> 00:42:26,220
(9 350 USD or 6 650 Pounds)

903
00:42:23,060 --> 00:42:26,220
Close to 1 million yen.

904
00:42:26,220 --> 00:42:29,330
Do you feel satisfied with your purchases?

905
00:42:29,330 --> 00:42:30,770
Very much so

906
00:42:30,440 --> 00:42:32,760
Really?

907
00:42:31,710 --> 00:42:33,680
The cost is high...

908
00:42:32,810 --> 00:42:35,690
They are used to the high price point

909
00:42:33,680 --> 00:42:37,680
but the customers seems satisfied with paying it.

910
00:42:38,040 --> 00:42:42,630
Furthermore, as we continue our investigation,

911
00:42:42,630 --> 00:42:47,040
We have discovered a number of genre specific point cards.

912
00:42:48,070 --> 00:42:49,490
To begin with

913
00:42:49,490 --> 00:42:54,590
at a West African traditional drumming practice course for "Djembe"

914
00:42:54,940 --> 00:42:57,120
1000 yen is equal to 1 point

915
00:42:56,210 --> 00:42:58,670
Their sensei sure is convincing

916
00:42:57,120 --> 00:42:59,950
If you save 100,000 yen worth of points...

917
00:42:59,950 --> 00:43:03,100
You receive a big Djembe drum

918
00:43:03,100 --> 00:43:05,880
However, the course is only once a week

919
00:43:05,880 --> 00:43:10,230
and one lesson is 2000 yen, so it will take 50 weeks to save the points.

920
00:43:10,340 --> 00:43:15,970
Which means if you go to every class without skipping a week, it will take 350 days.

921
00:43:15,970 --> 00:43:19,210
In addition, the expiration date on the offer is in 2 years.

922
00:43:19,210 --> 00:43:20,600
A limit...

923
00:43:20,370 --> 00:43:22,370
With this ridiculous setting...

924
00:43:22,370 --> 00:43:28,340
...no one has been able to obtain the prize.

925
00:43:28,340 --> 00:43:29,950
You should have the points...

926
00:43:29,950 --> 00:43:32,080
by May of next year right? If you keep saving?

927
00:43:32,080 --> 00:43:34,360
Yeah, if I keep at this rate.

928
00:43:34,960 --> 00:43:40,140
Moving on, our next point card comes from this cemetery

929
00:43:40,140 --> 00:43:44,440
Our point card is called "Mairi Point Card". If you go around the cemetery once...

930
00:43:44,440 --> 00:43:49,080
You get 30 points.

931
00:43:49,560 --> 00:43:54,260
"Mairi Point". Combining the names "Mairi" and "Mile"

932
00:43:49,560 --> 00:43:54,260
(To pray)

933
00:43:54,260 --> 00:43:58,690
(Pray mile points)

934
00:43:54,260 --> 00:43:58,690
It comes together to form a hilarious name.

935
00:43:57,120 --> 00:44:00,700
Don't bully them

936
00:43:58,690 --> 00:44:00,760
If you go around the gravesite 40 times...

937
00:44:00,760 --> 00:44:04,130
You can receive flowers worth 1200 yen.

938
00:44:04,890 --> 00:44:08,790
A point card that will truly make your ancestors happy.

939
00:44:09,230 --> 00:44:14,230
Others: A candy store which will give a 50 yen off coupon if you come 20 times.

940
00:44:14,520 --> 00:44:17,800
A cycle track and bike store which

941
00:44:17,800 --> 00:44:20,270
will give you a "beckoning cat" if you come 240 times.

942
00:44:20,270 --> 00:44:22,620
Furthermore, a snake cafe

943
00:44:22,620 --> 00:44:25,690
which will let you touch the snakes as much as you want if you come 20 times.

944
00:44:25,980 --> 00:44:29,480
There are many special point cards indeed

945
00:44:29,480 --> 00:44:33,520
And there is one within those that is even more special

946
00:44:33,720 --> 00:44:37,150
Or rather, more like an insane point card

947
00:44:53,660 --> 00:44:58,210
An everyday goods shop in Saitama prefecture, Cosucoji

948
00:44:55,610 --> 00:44:58,210
C-cosu?

949
00:44:58,210 --> 00:45:01,260
In this store, 1000 yen equals 1 point.

950
00:45:01,260 --> 00:45:04,020
And 60,000 yen will allow you to

951
