956
00:45:11,570 --> 00:45:15,340
Oh really... is that it?

957
00:45:13,070 --> 00:45:15,340
Yup, that's it.

958
00:45:15,340 --> 00:45:17,800
There have been a few people who have done it.

959
00:45:17,800 --> 00:45:20,270
Oh really?

960
00:45:18,210 --> 00:45:20,270
Yeah, just a few people.

961
00:45:20,660 --> 00:45:22,990
Ibaragi Dialect Lesson

