00:45:22,990 --> 00:45:24,960
Have people saved up for this one?

963
00:45:24,960 --> 00:45:26,340
No, not at all

964
00:45:26,340 --> 00:45:30,450
No one has exchanged for this option, but you keep it on there?

965
00:45:27,260 --> 00:45:30,450
Yeah, I'm leaving it on there just in case someone does want it, I think it'll be interesting, you know?

966
00:45:30,450 --> 00:45:31,560
Ahahaha

