00:46:16,590 --> 00:46:19,750
It costs 9 million yen

984
00:46:19,750 --> 00:46:24,460
An inconceivable amount, this is a hellish privilege.

985
00:46:24,080 --> 00:46:27,110
This is so stupid...

986
00:46:24,860 --> 00:46:26,220
There you have it

